my_discord_bot/
├── bot.py              # Main bot file (setup, cog loading, core events)
├── .env                # Bot token (DO NOT SHARE)
├── requirements.txt    # Python dependencies
├── config/             # Folder to store server configurations (will be created)
│   └── (guild_id).json # Example: 123456789012345678.json
├── cogs/               # Folder for Cogs (feature modules)
│   ├── __init__.py     # Makes 'cogs' a Python package
│   ├── moderation.py   # Kick, ban, timeout, warn, clear, lock, slowmode
│   ├── utility.py      # Help, userinfo, serverinfo, avatar, ping, roleinfo
│   ├── verification.py # Verification button, role assignment, related commands
│   ├── logging.py      # Event logging (joins, leaves, mod actions), welcome/goodbye
│   └── fun.py          # Poll, coinflip, diceroll, etc.
└── utils/              # Optional: Folder for shared utility functions
    └── __init__.py
    └── config_manager.py # Helper for loading/saving JSON configs
    └── duration_parser.py # Helper for parsing duration